PAGE 1 CONTINUED - SESSION GUIDE:
Label: &quot;Session Guide · 13 Sessions · Short &amp; Crisp&quot; with line divider
Grid: 3 columns, gap 1px with border color #1B3329/8%, rounded 20px overflow hidden, each card bg #FFFEF9, padding 22px, min-height 168px
